GENERAL CONDITIONS
• All participants should read the rules carefully.
• For the awards, a total of 10,000,000 IXIRCOIN will be allocated and distributed gradually.
• You must be over 18 years of age in order to participate in the award campaign.
• The campaign will take 20 weeks.
• The awards will be distributed gradually within 4 weeks of the completion of the ICO sales.
• Tasks performed during the campaign (shares, articles, videos, publicity... etc.) you will need to register your own account at the web site with links in it. Within the framework of the rules, the balance will be defined within the site for those who perform weekly tasks (corresponding to gift coins in the table).
• If you are found to be cheating, you will be removed from the award program.
• Only full membership requirements are required to receive a membership bonus.
• When you perform tasks on sharing sites such as YouTube, Twitter, Facebook, LinkedIn, Reddit you need to add it to your profile page on the website (www.ixircoin.com). Those who perform their tasks according to the rules will be rewarded according to the order of addition to the website. There won’t be stakes.
• All members who qualify for the awards will be notified by e-mail, in the news section of the site and on the Bitcoin Talk page every week.
• The participants who wish to participate in the BMW raffle must have 1000 IXIRCOIN. Each 1000 IXIRCOIN will qualify for 1 raffle. When the amount of IxirCoin they have is divided by 1000, the right of raffle will appear. Participants in social media promotion
are not out of this process. The IXIRCOIN that they deserve will qualify for 1 raffle with 1000 IXIRCOIN.
• There is a section on the profile page to monitor the raffle rights.
• We reserve the right to change the rules of the award program if we cannot reach the desired number of participants.
